                          <i class="fa fa-share"></i>1. Player can deposit there balance in Load Balance section.<br><br>2. Player can take withdrawal by setting a withdrawal request on your app.<br><br>3. Deposit and withdrawal request completed by support at any time.<br><br>4. Any wrong payment detail given by you, will not be considered in refund.<br><br>5. Once withdrawal is done, you don't have any authority to raise any query.<br><br>6. If withdrawal request go on pending, user must have to wait for 3days.<br><br>
                        </div>
